The presence of a quorum was announced by the Majority Leader and Acting President Pro Tempore (Council Member Cumbo).

There were 47 Council Members marked present at this virtual Stated Meeting.

At the time of this virtual Stated Meeting, there were four vacant seats in the Council pending the swearing-in of the certified winners of the following special non-partisan elections: 
February 2, 2021 in the 24th District (Queens); 
February 23, 2021 in the 31st District (Queens); 
March 23, 2021 in the 11th and 15th Districts (The Bronx).
